3. Backend requirements:

* create SQLAlchemy model
* create database migration
* create seed script
* create API endpoint:
  GET /job-roles
* return roles grouped by category

Example response:
{
"Web Development": [...],
"Data & AI": [...]
}

4. Frontend requirements:

* update job role dropdown
* display roles grouped by category
* allow user to select one role

5. Generate only:

* backend job role model
* seed data script
* API endpoint
* frontend dropdown integration

Do not modify resume upload logic yet.
